title: Gold-trimmed studded leather armour

properties.name: description
properties.value: Gold-trimmed studded leather armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Studded leather armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from easy Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.

content:
This player looks like a real stud in that armour.

Gold-trimmed studded leather armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Studded leather armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from easy Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.
